# Secrets / creds — never commit
*.env
.env
*.kubeconfig
*credentials*
*secret*
oauth.env
# Exception: the umbrella chart's Secret *template* is Helm syntax, not secret
# material (its dev-default values live in the committed values.yaml). Without
# this the chart is silently uninstallable (backing stores reference a Secret
# that never gets committed).
!charts/curie/templates/secrets.yaml
# Exception: the committed JSON Schema for `curie secrets list --json` output
# (#634). It describes the SHAPE of that result (a list of secret NAMES), never
# any secret material, and the schema contract test requires it committed.
# Without this the `*secret*` rule above silently drops it and CI goes red.
!cli/schema/secrets.schema.json
# Same exception for the per-agent connector-secret template + its render-
# assertion script (ADR-0009, #429): Helm syntax / a test, not secret material.
!charts/curie/templates/agent-connector-secrets.yaml
!charts/curie/ci/connector-secrets-assertions.sh

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# Rust
target/

# Kubernetes local artifacts
.kube/
*.kubeconfig

# Node
node_modules/
dist/
build/

# Local working files (plans, scratch, analysis) — never committed
.projects/

# Local Curie runner and turn state
.curie/

# Personal, in-progress agent bundles (sibling of examples/) -- `list-agents`
# and `deploy-local <folder>` read from here; never part of the repo proper.
agents/

# Big-plan server sidecars (belong with the .projects working copies, not the repo)
*.snapshot
*.comments.json

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp

# generated CLI manifest module (apps/ui codegen)
apps/ui/src/generated/
